# Hardware Board Roles

Do **not** guess which Arduino does what. Use this map:

| Board | Alias | Port (typical) | Firmware | Role |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Uno R3 | `/dev/arduino-stewart` | `ttyACM0` | `arduino/uim5756pm_stewart/` | 3-DOF Stewart tilt (UIM5756PM) |
| Uno R4 Minima | `/dev/arduino-modules` | `ttyACM1` | `arduino/servo_calib/` | Module-grid **servos AND LEDs** |

## Hard rules

- R4 is **not** LED-only and **not** the Stewart board.
- R3 is **not** the module PCA9685/servo board.
- Prefer `/dev/arduino-stewart` and `/dev/arduino-modules` over raw `ttyACM*`.
- Before flashing or smoke-testing, confirm with `ls -l /dev/arduino-*` and `arduino-cli board list`.

## Stewart pinout (Uno R3) — source of truth

Amazon / UIM344 Fig 0-6 cable colors (these motors have **no purple**):

| Wire | Function | Connect to |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Brown | COM | Arduino 5V |
| Gray | DIR | DIR pin |
| Yellow | PLS | PLS pin |
| Blue | ENA | ENA pin |
| Black (signal) | GND | Arduino GND |
| White / Green | TX / RX | leave unconnected |

| Axis | PLS (Yellow) | DIR (Gray) | ENA (Blue) |
| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: |
| 0 | D2 | D3 | D4 |
| 1 | D7 | D8 | D9 |
| 2 | D11 | D12 | D13 |

If firmware, README, or udev names disagree with this table, **fix the docs/code** — do not "correct" the hardware to match old docs.
